            <lg xml:id="TK30">
<l>antaṇa reṉpō raṟavōrmaṟ ṟevvuyirkkuñ</l>
<l>centaṇmai pūṇṭoḻuka lāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Men of dharma are called "Your Grace," for towards all living beings</l>
<l>they conduct themselves with rich cooling grace.</l>
